org.cloudgraph.hbase.scan

Class FuzzyRowKeyScanAssembler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.hbase.scan.FuzzyRowKeyScanAssembler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Assembler, HBaseFilterAssembler, FuzzyRowKey, RowKeyScanAssembler

    public class FuzzyRowKeyScanAssembler
extends java.lang.Object
implements RowKeyScanAssembler, FuzzyRowKey, HBaseFilterAssembler
    Assembles a composite fuzzy row key bytes / fuzzy info bytes pair where each field within the composite row keys are constructed based a set of query predicates.
    Since:
    0.5.3
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
    See Also:
    DataGraphConfig, TableConfig, UserDefinedField, PredefinedField, PreDefinedFieldName
